@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.cos((v1 + 0.11 / v2 + 0.14)))
    tmp = wp.sin((wp.abs(tmp + 0.90) * wp.cos(tmp + 0.51)))
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.exp(v1))
    v1 = (0.64 - 0.51)
    v2 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.73 / tmp + 0.10)) - (wp.sin(v2 + 0.04) / (v2 + 0.48 + v2 + 0.11)))
    tmp = 0.99
    data[tid] = v0
